@Yuki2718 I don't see the issue on my end with blocking `googlesyndication.com`. The issue comes from bait generic cosmetic rules and fetching HEAD requests of `fundingchoicemessages.com` (which is not blocked by default and only blocked by some other regional lists)

```javascript
try {
  await fetch(
    'https://fundingchoicesmessages.google.com/b/pub-1437333416759682',
    {
      method: 'HEAD',
      mode: 'no-cors',
      cache: 'no-store'
    }
  )
} catch (t) {
  r(!0),
  e()
}
```

